                        <interp inst="t18480131-name-350" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN PECK</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, H</hi> 87.) I produce a certificate of the prisoner's former conviction—(<hi rend="italic">read</hi>--<hi rend="italic">Convicted June</hi>, 1846, <hi rend="italic">and confined one month</hi>)—he is the person—he has been several times in custody since—he had twenty one days, and has also had six weeks.</p>
